        last_assistant_message: |-
            Here's what we have — Phase 1 is fully complete:

            ## Current State

            ### 4 Binaries (all in `bin/`)

            | Binary | Role |
            |--------|------|
            | `orchestrator` | Central hub — starts plugins, routes QUIC messages |
            | `storage-markdown` | Writes/reads files as `<!-- META {json} META -->` + Markdown |
            | `tools-features` | 34 feature-driven workflow tools |
            | `transport-stdio` | MCP JSON-RPC bridge (stdin/stdout → QUIC) |

            ### 6 Go Modules

            | Module | Path |
            |--------|------|
            | Proto generated code | `gen/go/` |
            | Plugin SDK (QUIC, mTLS, framing) | `libs/go/` |
            | Orchestrator service | `services/orchestrator/` |
            | Storage plugin | `plugins/storage-markdown/` |
            | Tools plugin (34 tools) | `plugins/tools-features/` |
            | Transport plugin | `plugins/transport-stdio/` |

            ### Tests: 66 unit + 1 E2E

            | Component | Tests |
            |-----------|-------|
            | Plugin SDK | 11 |
            | Orchestrator | 10 |
            | storage.markdown | 11 |
            | tools.features | 24 |
            | transport.stdio | 20 |
            | E2E (full flow) | 1 |

            ### E2E Flow (verified working)

            ```
            Agent (stdin JSON-RPC)
              → transport.stdio
                → orchestrator (QUIC)
                  → tools.features (create_feature)
                    → orchestrator (StorageWrite proxy)
                      → storage.markdown
                        → FEAT-XXX.md on disk
            ```

            ### 22 Specialized Agents (`.claude/agents/`)
            ### 17 Design Artifacts (`docs/artifacts/`)
            ### 7 Implementation Docs (`docs/implementation/01-07`)

            ### Quick Commands
            ```bash
            make build       # Build all 4 binaries
            make test        # Run 66 unit tests
            make test-e2e    # Full integration test
            make proto       # Regenerate proto code
            make clean       # Remove build artifacts
            ```

            Everything is under `github.com/orchestrated-mcp/framework`. Ready for Phase 2 whenever you are.
